history.content:
The goal of Virtual Boeing Day is to expose UC Berkeley students to passionate Boeing employees and showcase the many different careers that Boeing offers.

Virtual Boeing Day will consist of presentations from two executive speakers, Boeing Technical Fellows, and a UC Berkeley Alumni at Boeing Q&A Panel. More information about speakers and presentations will be given to accepted applicants after March 24th.

Virtual Boeing Day will be held on Friday, March 26th from 7:30am to 12:15pm. This application will close on Sunday, March 21st at 11:59p.m. You will be notified of your acceptance status to Virtual Boeing Day by no later than Wednesday, March 24th.

Application link: https://forms.gle/CifxHiD7jfEzXJr56


Boeing Day 2021 applications are live! Apply at https://forms.gle/CifxHiD7jfEzXJr56. Deadline is March 21st, 2021.
